N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5307.7 - Duration of license and registration

State Regulations

Casino vendor enterprise licenses, ancillary casino
vendor enterprise licenses and vendor registrations shall remain valid as set
forth in Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering and Breeding Law section
1327. Notes
